q1: What stadium does PSG play their home games?
a1: Parc des Princes is their home ground
a2: Paris SG wasn't founded by a single person.
a3: The founders were Guy Crescent, Henri Patrelle, and Pierre-Étienne Guyot.
a4: Qatar Investment Authority  have been Paris SG's owner since 2011.
q5: With the quality of players PSG has now, will they be able to win the champions league this season?
a5: They have the quality to do it, but there are strong competitors.
